    "The PRISMA diagram outlines each step of this workflow, including identification, screening, eligibility, and inclusion, ensuring reproducibility and clarity in the review process.",
    "In addition to these technological advances, Fig. 4, 5, and 6 visualize the research focus on olfactory and gustatory systems by presenting word clouds generated from the identified studies.",
    "The 100 most frequently used terms from each field were extracted to create these visualizations.",
    "This approach highlights emerging priorities and the thematic divergence between olfaction and gustation research.",
    "By focusing on the latest developments and innovations in these areas, we aim to offer a timely overview of the evolving AI landscape in sensory science."
